                                "response": "Thanks for taking the time to leave a review. \r\nWe're sorry you had such an experience during Summer Academy. Our goal is always to provide our students with a productive and successful lesson and surrounding experience, and of course our teachers are integral to that. \r\nWe do provide guidance for our schools to maximise scheduling efficiency while balancing staff wellbeing; and strongly encourage all our teachers to take breaks and rest when they can. Summer and Winter are peak periods and can be intense for all involved, and we're sorry that you feel you did not receive the support you needed. \r\nSalaries and compensation are regularly reviewed to be in line with industry standards; we will continue to do this. Similarly any bonus should be clearly understood, and we will work to address any gaps in knowledge or requirement or payment details.\r\nWe will also continue to work with our local and regional managers to ensure every member of staff has what they need to be both successful in the classroom and enjoy a balanced and healthy personal life.\r\nIn the meantime, and if you would like to share more, you are welcome to do so, confidentially, as teacher.welfare@ef.cn.\r\nThank you again.",
